# Elden Data

- **`client/`** — Vite + React 19 + TypeScript, TanStack Router/Form, Zustand, shadcn/ui, Tailwind v4, PocketBase JS SDK, i18next (en/fr)
- **`pb_migrations/`** — PocketBase collection migrations (JS)
- **`Dockerfile`** — builds client → `public/`, runs PocketBase on `:8090`
- **Dev**: `client/` → `pnpm dev` (Vite proxies `/api` → PocketBase); backend → `make dev` / `docker compose`

Follow conventions in `client-react.mdc` and `client-typescript.mdc` when editing the frontend.
